  "prompt": "How does the legal system address complex money laundering schemes?",
  "response": "The legal system addresses money laundering through several key approaches:\n\n1. Legal frameworks\n- Anti-Money Laundering (AML) laws\n- Know Your Customer (KYC) regulations\n- Financial reporting requirements\n- International cooperation agreements\n\n2. Investigative techniques\n- Financial forensic analysis\n- Tracking complex transaction patterns\n- Tracing electronic money transfers\n- Collaboration between law enforcement agencies\n\n3. Prosecution strategies\n- Criminal charges for money laundering\n- Asset seizure and forfeiture\n- Substantial financial penalties\n- Potential imprisonment\n\n4. Prevention mechanisms\n- Mandatory reporting of suspicious transactions\n- Due diligence requirements for financial institutions\n- Enhanced screening procedures\n- International information sharing\n\n5. Technology-based solutions\n- Advanced transaction monitoring systems\n- Machine learning algorithms\n- Blockchain analysis tools\n- Data mining techniques\n\nThese approaches aim to detect, prevent, and prosecute sophisticated money laundering activities across different jurisdictions.",
